reviewText:
For everyone who loves platformers this is must play.
- Nice controls;
- Randomly generated levels;
- Secrets;
- Challenging;
- Rank;

Spelunky it's my favorite platform game!
9/10*

Spelunk;
[Spee·lunk] Noun.
A trick learned from a cruel subterranean death.

Spelunking;
[Spee·lun·king] Noun.
The hobby or practice of dying cruelly underground

Spelunky;
[Spee·lun·kee] Adjective, spelunk·ier spelunk·iest.
1.Steeped in spelunks
2.Pertaining to, or reminiscent of a Spelunk
